  "10-5": {
    "id": "10-5",
    "instruction": "How to evaluate this rule:\nDuring the resume matching phase, automatically read all hard requirements from the 招聘需求, including 学历, 必备技能, 语言要求, 性别, and 年龄. Perform an item-by-item comparison of the candidate against each hard threshold as follows:\na) 学历: check whether the candidate’s highest_acquired_degree field in the Candidate object meets the JD最低学历要求 recorded in the Job_Requisition degree_requirement field;\nb) 必备技能: check whether the candidate’s skill list in the Resume skill_tags field contains every mandatory item listed in the Job_Requisition must_have_skills field;\nc) 语言要求: if the Job_Requisition language_requirements field specifies a 语言要求, check whether the candidate’s Resume language_skills and Resume certificate fields satisfy the required language type and minimum standard;\nd) 性别: if the Job_Requisition gender field specifies a 性别要求, check whether the Candidate gender field matches that requirement;\ne) 年龄: if the Job_Requisition age_range field specifies an 年龄范围要求, check whether the candidate’s age derived from the Candidate birth_date field falls within the allowed range.\nThis rule fires when any one of these hard requirements is not satisfied.\n\nWhat to do when this rule fires:\nMark the candidate as 不匹配. Populate the result field of the Candidate_Match_Result object with a 不匹配 status, and populate the reason field of the Candidate_Match_Result object with the specific non-compliant dimension and the exact cause. Immediately terminate the subsequent matching and recommendation flow, stop all further evaluation, and return immediately.\n\nHow to verify before moving on:\nConfirm that the Candidate_Match_Result result field indicates 不匹配, that the Candidate_Match_Result reason field accurately records the specific dimension and detailed cause of the mismatch, and that no further matching or recommendation steps have been performed.",
    "meta": {
      "sourceVersion": "unknown",
      "transformedAt": "2026-05-09T08:34:13.267Z",
      "transformedBy": "kimi-k2.6",
      "roundTripCheck": "failed",
      "originalProse": "系统在简历匹配阶段，自动执行以下操作：(1)读取该岗位需求中的全部硬性要求，包括学历、必备技能、语言要求、性别及年龄等；(2)逐项比对候选人与需求硬性门槛的匹配情况：a）学历：候选人学历等级是否达到JD最低学历要求；b）必备技能：候选人技能列表是否包含JD要求的全部必备技能项；c）语言要求：若招聘需求存在语言要求，候选人语言能力及证书是否满足需指定语言类型与最低标准；d）性别：若招聘需求存在性别要求，候选人性别是否符合；e）年龄：若招聘需求存在年龄范围要求，候选人年龄是否在允许范围内；(3)任一硬性要求不符，系统立即标记该候选人为不匹配记录具体不符合的维度及原因，并终止后续匹配与推荐流程；(4)全部硬性要求比对通过的简历，标进入后续评估环节。"
    }
  },
